thread.title: Jeff Kost
thread.title_full: Rackmount Solutions reviewed by Jeff Kost

author: Jeff Kost
title: Jeff Kost
text: Their shipper was horrible. Product was delivered as specified by Rackmount earlier than estimated, but the product sat in a transfer facility for a week + because the shipper was incompetent. We had to spend the money to pick up the product at the transfer facility because of this, which cost the project time and money. This isn't directly attributed to Rachmount, but it was still a black eye on the project.
